actions.text: Submitted in the Senate, considered, and agreed to without amendment by Voice Vote.

official_title: A resolution authorizing the printing of additional copies of a compilation containing the eulogies of the late Senator Warren G. Magnuson.

summary.text: Authorizes the printing as a Senate document a collection of statements made in tribute to the late Senator Warren G. Magnuson and published in the Congressional Record. Authorizes additional printing for the use of the Senate the lesser of 300 copies or such number as does not exceed a specified cost.

titles.title: A resolution authorizing the printing of additional copies of a compilation containing the eulogies of the late Senator Warren G. Magnuson.
